query_birthdate_from: select top (1) PerC.UniqueId, convert(varchar, PerC.BirthDate, 104) Ent from PersonCards PerC where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and PerC.BirthDate < '01.01.1985' and PerC.BirthDate > '01.01.1900' and day(PerC.BirthDate) > 1 and month(PerC.BirthDate) > 1 and dateadd(day, -1, PerC.BirthDate) in (select PerC.BirthDate from PersonCards PerC where PerC.IsDeleted != 1)

query_birthdate_to: select top (1) PerC.UniqueId, convert(varchar, PerC.BirthDate, 104) Ent2 from PersonCards PerC where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and PerC.BirthDate > '01.01.1990' and PerC.BirthDate < getdate() and day(PerC.BirthDate) > 1 and month(PerC.BirthDate) > 1 and dateadd(day, 1, PerC.BirthDate) in (select PerC.BirthDate from PersonCards PerC where PerC.IsDeleted != 1)
